The paper analyzes the linguistic structure of questions on Quora, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also looks into the perception of anonymity and personality traits of users, which could fall under social and information sciences (cs.SI), data mining (cs.SD), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and human-computer interaction (cs.SOC).
